values:
So i'm FINALLY done with my A.P.Psychology exam! WOOOOO go me! its such a releife to be done! Its kinda like a big weight off my shoulders. it felt so good i had to get ice cream! me, sarah, kayla, amanday and mellissa went to khops after to indulge and rejoyce for having been done offically with a.p. psychology tests. yay! We still have some paketeering to do, but for the most part we have nothing to do but watch movies unitl the end of the year. rock on. 
    so i'm supposed to be doing my econ presentation, but i just don't feel like it. i don't care that its gonna be late, i really don't at this point. all together now, senioritis! 
    I am however currently working on my present to everybody for graduation. i have to tell you all i hope you appreciate it, cause it sucks! i've been doing it for like 3 hours and i'm still not done with this part. ITs all good though, cause its gonna be PHAT when i'm done. remember that word phat? i think we should bring it back. it could make a perfect addition to my list of words that are fun to say. i also think we should start saying solid again, just cause, but we can talk about that after we add phat to our vocab again. one at a time you know. Toodles

Quote of the day: "so i was asnwering number one, and i started to write...you F**k wad!" 
     ~me

Man is it cold in here! I neeed my heater. I could really go for a hot tub (hint hint sam). So i SITLL havn't started to study for my A.P. exam, can we say procrastination? I just cna't bring myself to acctually sit down and study that mountin of stuff i have to know. its like there is no way i'm going to be able to learn it all, so why even bother? i think i know the reason why i'm so distracted. here it is ladies http://vindieselgallery.net/gallery/thumbnails.php?album=44 well, that and gabe decieded to instant message me from out of the blue tonight. i forgot how much i miss him. i wonder if he knows how much it kills me that he was talking about this sophomre he has this thing for. do guys ever know how much that sucks when they talk about their love intrests that arn't you? well i can always drown out my sorrows in vin. i'm gonna go watch the fast and the furrious and try to study. emphasis on try . toodles.

Hurray for me! I have finally joined the rank of people with one of these live journal thingies! WOOOOOOOOO go me! yeah dude, i ROCK! I'd like to start out by thanking god for the opporntunity to make this live journal. I wanna thank my mom, cause if it weren't for her, i wouldn't be here. A big thanx goes out to all of the fine people at livejournal for makeing the site. A specail shout out goes to nat and sam for helping me create my livejournal. Oh yeah, i and i wanna thank the fans, cause if it weren't for them i wouldn't be anywhere near what i am today. I love you and goodnight.
